N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4403.6 - Transmission equipment

State Regulations

The plan of operation shall include a written description
and a blueprint or diagram of the locations in branch offices of all equipment
capable of the transmission of information, whether mechanical, electrical, manual or electronic. Notes
